title: 2.31 The Many Names of Jesus
itunes:title: The Many Names of Jesus
description: King of the Jews, Saviour, Son of Man, God, Son of God, Messiah and Christos, and Lord. The New Testament has many titles for Jesus. Let's investigate them.
